    "monthEnd": null,
    "dayEnd": null,
    "eventCategoryId": null,
    "importance": "notable",
    "description": "<p>The earliest known ruler of the land that would eventually become Equestria, Grogar was a mysterious tyrant emperor and creator of all monsters that roam Equus. Eventually, his tyranny was challenged by Gusty the Great and her unicorn warriors, who are theorized to have been an expedition from the north of Equestria. Gusty the Great was able to defeat Grogar after separating him from the source of his power: the Bewitching Bell. Grogar was thus banished to the Realm of Shadows, and his bell hidden by Gusty in the hopes that nobody could use it's evil power again</p>",
    "articleId": null,
